# CATEGORY 2: VAMPIRES
if {OPINIONS.sun_vampire} <= 1:
	king_sun: THESE PRETENTIOUS NIGHT CRAWLERS THINK THEY'RE SO ELEGANT! HIDING FROM THE SUN LIKE COWARDS! WHAT KIND OF RULER NEEDS DARKNESS JUST TO EXIST?!
	- They hide because your power is overwhelming. You dominate the sky.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 4, 20)
		king_sun: [speed=0.3] ...DAMN RIGHT I DO. [/speed] FINALLY SOMEONE GETS IT.
	- They just prefer night. Different environment, that's all.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 4, 0)
		king_sun: "DIFFERENT ENVIRONMENT." THAT'S A GENEROUS WAY TO SAY INFERIOR.
	- Honestly… they are more refined than you.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 4, -20)
		king_sun: [shake rate=20.0 level=6 connected=1] GET OUT. GET OUT RIGHT NOW. [/shake]
else:
	king_sun: VAMPIRES! THEY CALLED MY RADIANCE "OVERWHELMING." I THINK THEY MEANT IT AS PRAISE.
	- Of course it was praise. Your presence is impossible to ignore.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 4, 20)
		king_sun: EXACTLY. THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT I SAID. YOU UNDERSTAND ME.
	- Hard to tell with vampires.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 4, 0)
		king_sun: [speed=0.4] ...yeah. [/speed] HARD TO TELL. STILL COUNTS THOUGH.
	- That might've been criticism.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 4, -20)
		king_sun: [shake rate=10.0 level=4 connected=1] IT WAS NOT CRITICISM. [/shake] TAKE THAT BACK.

