	- Your power has purpose. Theirs is just instinct.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 5, 20)
		king_sun: PURPOSE. YES. WRITE THAT DOWN. THERE IS A DIFFERENCE.
	- They act on emotion more than planning.
		do DiplomacyManager.modify_opinion(0, 5, 0)
