else:
	king_sun: HEY! YOU WON'T BELIEVE WHAT JUST HAPPENED. I TALKED TO A PACK OF WEREWOLVES. ONE OF THEM SAID MY RAGE IS "HONEST." …NO ONE EVER SAYS THAT.
